NameBlamTag dw3\r3ach\objects\weapons\rifle\plasma_rifle\firing.effect reach\objects\weapons\rifle\plasma_rifle\fx\firing

PortTag dw3\r3ach\objects\weapons\rifle\plasma_rifle\plasma_rifle.model
PortTag dw3\r3ach\sound\weapons\plasma_rifle\prifle_heat_loop\prifle_heat_loop.sound_looping
PortTag dw3\r3ach\objects\weapons\rifle\plasma_rifle\animations\fp_spartan\fp_spartan.model_animation_graph
PortTag dw3\r3ach\objects\weapons\rifle\plasma_rifle\animations\fp_elite\fp_elite.model_animation_graph
